title: Don't Give Up || EP: 104
description:
Hey Rehabbers,
I just want to tell you sometimes you have to go through what you go through to prepare you for the GREATER that's meant for you. I hope this episode inspires you to never close the book of your life just because the chapter you're currently on isn't ideal. There's more to your life. Never forget that.
